  "title": "UX Tools 负责人：设计师如何把 Claude Code 用进日常工作？丨 Dive Club",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485192&idx=1&sn=77f2b316f2600ce89d8d8f59a2063f82",
  "date": "2026-01-14 14:18:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=483036c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaubJvugmGm218ry81z6KungOvJtqIVdKDrX6gXbGT03VF5yBHp71quJQVjuicmb5G157W8RqcfCXyxNy01I19kQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">我们每天为你更新硅谷最新的 AI 创业与科技播客总结，让你与前沿保持同频。</span><span leaf=\"\">全文约 4800 字，如果你现在没有时间，试试听文章播客</span><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/player/player?podcastId=019bbcd6-218c-78d9-b91c-fd9e4ca772a4&amp;openWithin=true\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听/X3qFAzPaSwdj6wq\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/aubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"140\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"0.24188790560471976\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-w=\"1017\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f807faf8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FaubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></a></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“如果你不知道如何用代码描述‘好品味’，就把大师的作品喂给 AI，让它去模仿。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“工程问题往往可以转化为直觉问题。别猜参数了，用控制面板去‘调’出感觉。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“Claude Code 不仅仅是写代码的工具，它本质上是你的超级实习生和电脑管家。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">到了 2026 年，设计师的角色正在发生质的变化。Kyle Xantos，UX Tools Labs 的负责人，给自己定下了一个目标：完全转型为一名利用 AI 进行构建的“设计工程师”。这次对话将深入探讨一些你可以在自己的设计工程中运用的具体策略。我们将介绍推荐的工具、工作流程，以及 Kyle 使用 Claude Code 构建设计工程“技能”的过程。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 1：利用视觉编辑器快速微调样式</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于 Cursor 最近推出的视觉编辑器，社区里的讨论非常热烈。它的定位很有意思：试图用设计师熟悉的 Figma 界面语言来包装代码编辑器。Cursor 似乎在说：“看，这些工具你都认识，设计和工程之间不应该有那么大的鸿沟。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">实际体验并没有那么完美，它还不是 Figma 的替代品。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Kyle 分享了他最近为朋友们制作的一个橄榄球比分竞猜应用的经历。以前他们用 Excel 表格或者雅虎的 App，体验都很一般。今年，Kyle 决定自己动手做一个。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“它并没有把 Figma 变成代码，这还没发生。但当你只是想微调间距或布局时，它是一个非常容易上手的胜利。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在开发过程中，Kyle 发现视觉编辑器最大的价值在于“微调”。比如，他觉得某个卡片的内边距有点多，看起来很累赘。在纯代码环境里，他可能需要去猜数值，改代码，保存，看效果，再改。但在 Cursor 的视觉模式下，他可以直接拖动参数，看着界面实时变化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“即时反馈”的感觉是设计师最需要的，它让你跳出了枯燥的“写提示词-等待生成”的循环，让你能直接上手“捏”界面。Kyle 目前的工作流是混合的：他在 Cursor 里打开终端运行 Claude Code 来处理复杂的逻辑，同时利用 Cursor 的内置浏览器和视觉编辑器来进行样式上的快速实验。这对于那些对终端命令行感到恐惧的设计师来说，是一个极佳的过渡方案。你依然在使用强大的 AI 能力，但界面更加友好，操作更加直观。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 2：建立隔离环境测试复杂组件</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多设计师在转行写代码时，容易犯一个错误：在一个庞大复杂的项目里直接尝试写新的组件。结果往往是不仅新功能没写好，还把原本运行正常的页面搞崩了，挫败感极强。Kyle 提出了一个非常实用的建议：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">建立你的“游乐场”。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你还没开始这样做，我强烈推荐你试试：当你脑海里有个想实现的效果却找不到现成的版本时，就为它专门建一个‘游乐场’。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 正在构建自己的个人网站，主题是一个“复古未来主义”的外星探索世界。他在设计一个视频播放的交互时，想要加入一个波形图的动效，用来指示声音的开关状态。他没有直接在主网站的代码里折腾，而是单独开了一个空白页面，甚至是一个独立的小项目，专门用来调试这个波形组件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个隔离的环境里，他可以肆无忌惮地尝试。他让 AI 生成了十几种不同的波形跳动模式：有的像是故障艺术，有的像是老式 CRT 显示器的扫描线，有的则是平滑的液态流动。他把这些效果排列在一起，像是一个专门的“波形图工作室”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">“当我找到那个完美的激活状态和静音状态后，我只需要把这段经过验证的代码复制回我的主项目里。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这种做法极大地降低了心智负担。你不需要担心搞坏现有的东西，你可以专注于打磨这一个细节。同样的逻辑，他还做了一个“全息投影仪”的组件，可以把普通的视频素材渲染出 3D 全息投影的效果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“游乐场”思维，其实就是把复杂问题拆解。当你需要实现一个脑海中模糊的视觉效果时，不要在复杂的业务逻辑里做，去旁边搭个积木，搭好了再搬回来。这对于那些不知道如何用专业术语描述动效的设计师来说，尤其管用——你不需要知道什么是“弹簧物理引擎”，你只需要在游乐场里试出来就行。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 3：通过投喂案例让 AI 复制审美</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">设计工程师和纯开发者的区别，往往在于审美。但如何让 AI 理解你的审美？Kyle 的方法简单粗暴：直接把大师的作品喂给 AI，让它“学会”这种风格。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我直接把那个推文链接丢给 Claude Code，告诉它：‘这个技术太棒了，我要把它应用到我的组件上，去搞定它。’ 它就真的去分析了链接，提取了代码片段，然后应用到了我的设计里。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">他在推特上看到设计师 James McDonald 分享了一种多层阴影的技术。这种技术不是简单地加一个黑框，而是通过叠加三层不同透明度、不同扩散范围的阴影，来模拟出一种极具质感的、类似物理边框的效果。这种细腻的效果，如果你试图用语言去描述给 AI 听，大概率会得到一个又黑又粗的框。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 甚至在一个给三岁儿子开发的幼儿识字游戏里应用了这个技术。那些卡片的边缘处理得极其精致，完全不像是一个普通的儿童应用。他并没有手动去 Figma 里一层层调阴影参数，而是让 AI 理解了“James McDonald 风格”，然后自动生成。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">更进一步，Kyle 利用一个名为“Compound Engineering”的插件，将这种模仿系统化了。他非常推崇 Jay Tompkins 和 Yakob 等极简主义开发者的代码风格——代码干净、逻辑清晰、动效丝滑。他收集了这几位大神的大量 CodePen 案例和博客文章，打包喂给了 Claude Code。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">他创建了一个专门的“技能”。他对 AI 说：“你要学习这些人的编码风格和设计思考方式。从现在开始，你就是我的‘视觉审计员’。”每当 Kyle 写完一段代码，他就可以召唤这个 AI 代理：“用 Jay Tompkins 的标准，帮我检查一下这个组件的交互代码。哪里做得不够优雅？哪里可以更丝滑？”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种做法把抽象的“好品味”变成了一套可执行的代码标准。你不需要自己成为 CSS 大师，你只需要知道谁是大师，然后让 AI 去模仿他们。随着时间的推移，你可以不断向这个“技能包”里添加新的参考链接，让你的 AI 助手越来越懂你的口味。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 4：使用可视化面板调整动效参数</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在做动效时，设计师最痛苦的莫过于调参数。弹簧系数是 120 还是 130？延迟是 0.2 秒还是 0.3 秒？在代码里改数字，不仅慢，而且很难直观感受到变化。Kyle 强烈推荐了一个神器：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Leva</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我不需要知道具体的贝塞尔曲线数值。我只需要拖动滑块，直到那种‘感觉’对了，然后直接把数值写死在代码里。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个可以浮在页面上的参数控制面板。你只需要告诉 Claude Code：“帮我给这个动画加一个 Leva 控制面板，我想调整速度、摩擦力、透明度。”AI 就会自动帮你把这些变量绑定到面板上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 在复刻他父亲最爱的“月球着陆器”游戏时，就大量使用了这个技巧。为了让飞船卡片的悬停效果看起来既有科技感又不失趣味，他设计了一个线条从四角向中心汇聚的动画。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">“我不需要知道具体的贝塞尔曲线数值。我只需要拖动滑块，直到那种‘感觉’对了。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这种像调音台一样的操作方式，让他在几分钟内就锁定了一个完美的动效参数，然后直接把数值写死在代码里。Will King 曾对他说，这是成为设计工程师最简单的捷径。它把工程问题转化为了直觉问题。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 5：精简上下文，保持 AI 专注</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着项目变得越来越大，很多人发现 AI 似乎变“笨”了。它开始忘记你之前的指令，或者给出的代码充满了幻觉。Kyle 指出，这通常是因为我们给 AI 的上下文太杂乱了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“把所有东西都塞进一个全局的 claude.md 文件是个误区。这会挤占它的记忆空间，让它在处理当前任务时分心。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多新手喜欢把所有的项目文档、设计规范、API 接口都塞进那个全局的 `claude.md` 文件里。他们觉得给 AI 的信息越多越好。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">这是一个误区。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;`claude.md` 会一直占据 AI 的记忆空间。如果里面塞满了你现在根本不需要的后端数据库结构，而你正在写前端 CSS，这些无关信息就是噪音。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 的建议是：保持全局文件极其精简。只放那些绝对通用的规则（比如“永远使用 TypeScript”）。具体的规则应该下放到项目文件夹，甚至是子文件夹里。比如，在 `components` 文件夹里放一个说明文档，专门教 AI 怎么写组件；在 `api` 文件夹里放一个文档，专门解释接口。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">你需要像管理员工一样管理 AI 的注意力。给它当前任务所需的最少且最准确的信息，它的表现会好得多。不要指望一个文件能解决所有问题，那种“一劳永逸”的配置单在快速迭代的 AI 时代往往几个月就过时了。与其迷信某个博主的“终极配置”，不如学会这套按需分配上下文的思路。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 6：设立“调优日”专门升级工作流</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在日常工作中，我们往往为了赶进度而沿用旧的习惯，哪怕明知道有个新工具可能更好用。Kyle 提出了一个强制性的概念：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“调优日”。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你能每周哪怕只留出半天，不准做生产性的工作，只用来优化你的设置，尝试那个大家都在谈论的新插件，你会发现长期收益是巨大的。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">每周抽出半天时间（比如周五下午），在这段时间里，</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">严禁做任何推进具体项目进度的活。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这半天只用来做“磨刀”的事：整理乱七八糟的文件结构，尝试那个收藏了很久的新插件，或者试玩一下新的工作流。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 经常利用这半天时间做一些“无用”但好玩的东西，比如给儿子做一个 iPad 上的画画板，或者完善他的外星人网站。正是这些没有客户压力的时刻，让他掌握了像 Leva 这样的神器，或者搞懂了 Compound Engineering 的复杂配置。保持好奇心和玩耍的心态，是避免被技术浪潮淹没的最好救生圈。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">方法 7：组合工具，把 AI 当作系统管家</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，Kyle 分享了他的工具组合策略。对于预算有限的个人开发者，他推荐了一个高性价比的组合：Factory（20 美元）+ Claude Code。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Claude Code 可以做太多不只是写代码的事了。它可以是你的 Claude Computer，帮你整理文档、管理 Linear 任务，甚至充当你的超级实习生。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Factory 就像是 Cursor 的一个强力替代品，它集成了多种模型。Kyle 发现，</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro 模型在处理 UI 生成时表现出奇地好</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，甚至优于 Claude。所以他会用 Factory 配合 Gemini 来快速搭建界面，然后切换到 Claude Code 来处理复杂的逻辑和架构。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，要打破思维定势：Claude Code 不仅仅是一个代码工具，它是一个能够操作你电脑文件系统的智能体。Kyle 展示了一个非常开脑洞的用法：他用 Claude Code 来管理自己的 Obsidian 笔记库。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">他可以对 AI 说：“帮我把最近这几篇笔记整理一下，提取出里面提到的所有 AI 工具，单独列一个清单。”或者连接到任务管理软件 Linear：“帮我把所有状态为‘已完成’但还没归档的任务卡片都清理掉。”只要涉及到文本处理、文件整理、数据提取这类繁琐的杂活，你都可以丢给它。这才是“Claude Computer”概念的真正含义——它不是一个聊天机器人，它是你的超级实习生。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">结语：去做个构建者</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kyle 的 2026 年愿景很简单：成为一名构建者。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个时代，设计师最危险的状态是停留在“画图”的舒适区，等待工程师来还原你的像素。工具已经准备好了，门槛已经降得足够低。不管是通过 Cursor 微调样式，还是通过 Claude Code 编写逻辑，核心都在于你是否有动手的意愿。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要纠结于该学哪一个工具，也不要担心自己的代码不够优雅。正如 Kyle 所说：“每个人都有自己的工作台。”找到适合你手感的工具，建立你的游乐场，每周留出一点时间磨刀，然后开始构建。你脑海中的那个世界，现在真的可以被你亲手创造出来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“Designer's toolkit for Claude Code”丨Dive Club</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\">原视频：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcLz3ikw-n0&amp;t=517s\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcLz3ikw-n0&amp;t=517s</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细介绍了 UX Tools 负责人 Kyle Xantos 如何利用 Claude Code 和 Cursor 等 AI 工具，通过视觉微调、隔离测试、审美克隆及参数可视化等策略，实现从设计师向设计工程师的转型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细介绍了 UX Tools 负责人 Kyle Xantos 如何利用 Claude Code 和 Cursor 等 AI 工具，通过视觉微调、隔离测试、审美克隆及参数可视化等策略，实现从设计师向设计工程师的转型。",
  "summary": "文章探讨了在 2026 年 AI 深度介入开发的背景下，设计师如何利用 Claude Code 等工具重塑工作流。核心策略包括：利用 Cursor 视觉编辑器进行样式的即时微调；建立独立的“游乐场”环境测试复杂组件以降低心智负担；通过向 AI 投喂大师案例来克隆特定审美风格；使用 Leva 等可视化面板将抽象的动效参数调节转化为直觉操作。此外，作者强调了精简 AI 上下文的重要性，并建议设立专门的“调优日”来优化工具链。最终，文章鼓励设计师打破“画图”舒适区，利用 AI 成为具备构建能力的“设计工程师”。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "建立隔离的“游乐场”环境来开发和测试复杂组件。",
      "explanation": "在独立项目中调试新功能可避免破坏主项目逻辑，降低挫败感，让设计师能专注于视觉效果的极致打磨。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过投喂大师案例和代码风格，让 AI 学习并复制特定审美。",
      "explanation": "将优秀设计师的案例链接或代码库提供给 AI，使其成为“视觉审计员”，把抽象的品味转化为可执行的代码标准。"
    },
    {
